				\begin{document}$${\mathcal{R}}_{0}$$\end{document}R0 values between 2.4 and 3.18, with early death rates 30 times apart. Even further, our findings highlight how models of direct and indirect/environmental transmission can provide comparable results, rendering it easy to conflate routes of transmission9,61,62.
